Package ru.tinkoff.qa.neptune.selenium.content.management

Annotation Interface SwitchToWindow

@Retention(RUNTIME) @Target({TYPE,METHOD}) public @interface SwitchToWindow
Defines a browser window/tab to switch to

    • index

      int index
      Returns:
      an index of a browser window/tab to switch to. The minimal value of 0
      Default:
      -1

    • title

      String title
      Returns:
      a title/fragment or regexp of a title of a browser window/tab to switch to
      Default:
      ""

    • url

      String url
      Returns:
      a url/fragment or regexp of a url which is loaded in a browser window/tab to switch to
      Default:
      ""
